Query reactome for all participating genes in a set of pathways

Source: R/query_reactome_pathways.R
query_participating_genes.Rd

Get all genes participating in the provided list of reactome pathway identifiers.

query_participating_genes(pathways)

Arguments

pathways

character vector of valid reactome IDs

Value

character vector of ensembl IDs of the genes participating in any of the input pathways.

Examples

query_participating_genes("R-HSA-425407")
